name: Itelios at GitHub
body:
Feel free to clone and use our project : 

* iLeapLib - a simple objective-c library which use LeapMotion websocket server.
* LeapMotion-Proxy - a  simple proxy to allow the diffusion of LeapMotion websocket message's to another port and another IP than `localhost`
* LeapPong - a simple 2D Game using LeapMotion
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
